author: "YNWA" The Story of Liverpool FC
text: Liverpool played in their 1st #FACup final #OnThisDay  in 1914 where we lost to Burnley 1-0 in the last final staged at #CrystalPalace. We lost again in 1950, and it was only in 1965 that we finally won the famous old trophy with that famous Ian St John diving header. #LFC https://t.co/IyNyr7kB8S
